criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  healthy individuals aged 60-80 years old, of both sexes/genders

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  no recent weight loss and extreme dietary behaviors;

          -  no history of gastrointestinal disease, chronic constipation, chronic/acute diarrhea,
             autoimmune disease, coronary disease, liver and/or kidney malfunction;

          -  no consumption of antibiotics two months prior to the initiation of the intervention;

          -  no consumption of probiotics and/or prebiotics and/or dietary fiber supplements two
             weeks prior to the initiation of the intervention.
